  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1060">
<l>irappāṉ vekuḷāmai vēṇṭu nirappiṭumpai</l>
<l>tāṉēyuñ cāluṅ kari</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who begs ought not to be angry (at a refusal) for even the misery of (his own) poverty should be a sufficient reason (for so doing).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
